This is a GIMP plugins script and accompanying Bash shell script for
batch-processing texture images to produce normalmaps.

Requirements

GIMP 2.4: http://gimp.org
GIMP Normalmap plugin: http://nifelheim.dyndns.org/~cocidius/normalmap

Installation

In this directory, simply run:
make install

Usage

batch-normalmaps ~/.quake2world/textures/mine/*.tga
